latestIgtvVideos.title: Mr & Mrs Goddard - 02/10/20
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Yesterday we celebrated (hard) the beautiful marriage of my sister, Amber @amber_nicole_capewell & my new brother @e.goddard4 🤍 I know it wasn’t the day you’d planned ( 🖕🏼covid) but it was unbelievably beautiful nonetheless and I’m so proud of you both. I couldn’t love you both anymore. I don’t need to wish you a happy future because I know it’ll be bloody wonderful either way! So here’s a soppy video I made of your day, I’ll try make another next year but I think I’ll trip down the aisle and be THAT bridesmaid. Anyway, have a big old cry & I hope you love it xxx

latestIgtvVideos.title: PAINTING IN PROGRESS : SINGLE LINE PALM
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My first IGTV showing you something new & something old. Working on a much larger scale with this work is something new to me & my single line is one of my oldest and favourite ways to work. Here's a little insight into the creativity behind my work. Let me know what you think and any new suggestions. I can't wait to shoot on this! View my artwork on https://www.instagram.com/tuula.rose/

MUSIC : LOW TIDE BY DRAMA

latestPosts.caption: The final garden reveal ~ we couldn’t be happier with how this space turned out 🌿 from the dining area for long summer evenings to the seating area to lounge as we cook on the Kamado bbq. We really have bought our vision board to life after lots of hard work & gorgeous furniture from @westelmuk

& just like that, my baby is ONE 🤍 I have so many words to describe this last year, which I’ll write up in another post. But for now, this boy is simply the best thing that ever happened to me. Thank you for making life so wonderful my not so baby boy 🤍 thank you so much @cutterandsquidge for his first taste of cake 😍

latestPosts.caption: Endless summer evenings 🌞 made dreamy with this garden dining space, thanks to @westelmuk family 🫶🏼 Can’t wait to spend warm nights out here, under the willow tree with birdsong in the air, watching the world go by… AD

The first of the garden series: summer hosting 🌞 A peek into our newly finished garden, designed as the perfect space for relaxed entertaining with @westelmuk. On the menu: griddled flat peach, burrata, rocket & prosciutto salad, fresh sourdough, and balsamic, served with a glass of champagne. Tablescaped with @westelmuk from the perfect champagne coupe,  sardine shaped salt & pepper to the comfiest dining chairs, every detail made lingering long into the evening a must. This is summer hosting we’ve been dreaming of 🙌🏼 AD
